DOCUMENT();        # This should be the first executable line in the problem.

loadMacros(
"PG.pl",
"PGbasicmacros.pl",
"PGchoicemacros.pl",
"PGanswermacros.pl",
"PGauxiliaryFunctions.pl"
);

TEXT(beginproblem());
$showPartialCorrectAnswers = 1;

$m = random(2,5,1);
$a = random(1,4,1);
$b = random(5,8,1);
$m1 = $m+1;
$m2 = $m+2;
$t = $b-$a;
$n = $a*$b;

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
Factor the polynomial \(t^$m2+$t t^$m1-$n t^$m\). Your answer can be written as
\(t^N(t+A)(t+B)\) where \(A \lt B\). $BR
\(N\) equals:
\{ans_rule(10) \}
$BR
EOT

$ans = $m;
ANS(num_cmp($ans));

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
and \(A\) equals:
\{ans_rule(10) \}
$BR
EOT

$ans =  -$a;
ANS(num_cmp($ans));

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
and \(B\) equals:
\{ans_rule(10) \}
$BR
EOT

$ans =  $b;
ANS(num_cmp($ans));

ENDDOCUMENT();        # This should be the last executable line in the problem.
